headline: 4 chip stocks well positioned for Trump's 100% tariff threat
summary: President Trump has threatened 100% tariffs on semiconductors except for companies that are building in the US. Bernstein managing director and senior analyst Stacy Rasgon joins Market Domination with Yahoo Finance Markets Reporter Josh Schafer to share the four semiconductor names he believes are well-positioned despite Trump's threats. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination.
